						<tr>
							<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">When you hit 20, you can talk to Ian Cathlan in Qeynos Harbor to work on quests for armor pieces.  You can also talk to Hawl Ruksif in the Keep of the Ardent Needle there in Antonica for the Heritage Quest for the Dwarven Work Boots.  Eventually, once you start hunting in Thundering Steppes, you can learn giant language and get the quest for the Polished Granite Tomahawk.  You can't use the Tomahawk until 32 but it is a fine weapon.<br />_________________<br /><img src="http://www.mausturm.com/EQ2/images/dingsig1.jpg"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
