						<tr>
							<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">There are two ways to learn languages.  The first is to buy them from the scribes located in the various little towns around Qeynos or Freeport.
<br />

<br />
This will get you many of the player race languages.
<br />

<br />
The other way is through quests.  The quests start when you examine the first piece of what you need.
<br />

<br />
For the giants I believe that it is a totem.  For goblins it is a territory marker.  For lizardmen it is  a thulian puzzle box.  For... well you get the idea.  The items are body drops off the appropriate type of creatures.  You want to examine them immediately as they are LORE and NO DROP.
<br />

<br />
I hope this helps,<br />_________________<br />Andas
<br />
50 Swashbuckler
<br />
60 Jeweler</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
						</tr>
					</table></td>
				</tr>
